exceptions.exn: In environment pos_invert_t := fun n : nat => match n as n0 return ((pos n0 -> Type) -> Type) with | 0 => fun _ : pos 0 -> Type => True | S n0 => fun P : pos (S n0) -> Type => (P pos0 * (forall p : pos n0, P (pos_nxt p)))%type end : forall n : nat, (pos n -> Type) -> Type n : nat P : pos n -> Type H : pos_invert_t P p : pos n Unable to unify "pos_invert_t P" with "P p".
